data.description: Come enjoy this country living home that sits on an acre but is still close to the city! This adorable starter home features: 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, dining area, living room and den! The primary bedroom is separate from the other two bedrooms and features a walk in closet, claw foot tub and a tiled shower. The kitchen features stainless steel appliances, a gas range, a large pantry, open window to the den and a hidden closet! The dining room opens to the living room and den! The secondary bathroom has been completely remodeled to include a claw foot tub! The other two bedrooms have ample sized closet space and an office/play room/ flex room that separates the two of them. This home has been updated with vinyl replacement windows as well! The outside space is perfect for gardening, a small hobby farm or just about anything you would like! The backyard is fully fenced.  There are two decks on the back of the house with one being covered.
